Awakening: A Author's Mindset

This story was a labour of love between myself and the artist. The original plot changed a dozen times, several scenes were added to flesh out Lauren's journey (like the sex scene at the office with Ms. Martinez) and everything that included Anastasia, who wasn't in the original plot at all. Oddly, even naming her Anastasia occurred several pages before I decided to add some references to 50 Shades Freed; it just happened to be on heavy television preview as I wrote this).

Anyway, below you will see some photos that didn't work for some reasons I will explain and for the first time ever, a complete deleted scene that was pulled for continuity and characterization purposes. I finally understand why movie directors talk about scenes that were good, but which hurt the flow of the story or simply didn't work.

Obviously these will make almost no sense if you haven't already read the marathon journey of Lauren's sexual self-discovery in Blackmailed MILF: A Submissive Journey.

TASK 1: PUBLIC DILDO FUCKING

The first scene was critical to set the tone for who Lauren was and how, when it came right down to it, not only was she submissive, she was also unable to control her sexual hunger. It was also important to get the reader drawn into Lauren's plight but also to be drawn into the illustrations. I think we achieved that.

Public Pleasure:

The original photos taken of Lauren pleasuring herself in public had her clearly enjoying the task. But this didn't seem believable; she was being blackmailed. She was angry. She was doing this because she was being forced, not for her own sexual enjoyment (which will come later). So it was re-written and re-illustrated to make her appear more miserable, to make it clear to her blackmailer she was not an eager participant in this. That, of course, is shattered when she ends up pleasuring herself in the car, but she assumed the blackmailer wouldn't know she was doing this... that obeying him had turned her on.





Car Masturbation

Both the artist and I liked the idea of Lauren learning the blackmailer was sometimes watching her. Yes, it made it creepier that way, but it also was intriguing to us. During task one she has completed the assigned task, and as will happen often in the story, she finds herself doing something sexual that wasn't assigned, (such as fucking the black guy in the glory hole during task two). This time she masturbates because she's gotten so horny from completing the public masturbation task. In the story an adapted clothed version appears, but originally we had it that she was so overcome with lust that she ripped off her dress and pleasured herself.

This, in retrospect, seemed too extreme, especially on day one of the seven tasks. It was important that we see that doing the tasks turn her on, as this will be an underlying theme throughout, that no matter how badly she wants to hate the tasks, her body, her libido and her submissive nature betray her.

Yet, pleasuring herself naked in an alley in broad daylight seemed a bit much for our reserved teacher, especially this early in her awakening.



