TASK 5: CUM WALK

This scene was the simplest to write. My biggest concern was it was definitely simpler than spying on her daughter. Yet, walking in public with the risk of bumping into someone she knew made it, I think, slightly more challenging for her than the previous task.

That said, only a few pictures were created for this scene and they were all used.

TASK 6: STRIP CLUB

This task was set up from tasks three and five and would push her further, as by this point she had not only accepted her sexual journey, but was enjoying it. It was originally supposed to enhance her sexual submission and willingness to do almost anything to set up the extreme task seven.

What you are about to read isn't a deleted photo, but a complete deleted scene that would have taken place immediately after Lauren finishes her strip tease. In the finished version she ends up in an intimate, somewhat more romantic, scene with Anastasia where the romantic plot that ended up becoming important to the story begins.

That was not the original plan. Originally, Lauren was to get fucked by strangers and end up back onstage with Anastasia for a kinky lesbian performance. But that didn't make as much sense in the end, for Lauren's journey of sexual exploration.

This is the ultimate example where a character drives the story. So instead of a random threesome, Lauren insisted on having an intimate lesbian scene.

I also was concerned I was turning her into a simple slut who just fucked anybody, anytime, and that was not the characterization I wanted for Lauren. She is a strong woman, although submissive, who is simply exploring her sexuality after years of a sexually dormant marriage. She is accepting who she is, discovering what she wants and is enjoying the journey of rediscovering, or perhaps discovering, who she really is.

The scene you are about to read even included a subplot that would have potentially changed Lauren's career choice, and that too seemed a bit too farfetched (albeit in a story where the entirety is a bit far-fetched). Also, I have to admit, the plot of this scene seemed forced and less natural than the rest of the story.

Hopefully you will agree that the romantic, yet kinky sex, between Anastasia and Lauren was a more believable and for Lauren, rewarding choice.

